name: Unlock the Wisdom
description:
Unlock the wisdom

Frame by frame,
Layer by layer,
Formed to create an encrypted code to secure the function of the natural machinary system.

The source are the same,
Either in good or bad applications
System will works naturally and flawlessly whoever the user.
The problem is always on the user.

Everyone wants to conquer the source

The ancestor has made systems to make these thing sustains forever.
They made less writings, because they understand, the history was made by the winner, and writings could be interupted.
The data was hid in all over the place,
From the arts, buildings, dances, carvings, illustrations, stories, myths, clothings, languages, poets etc.

These are the wisdom of the ancestors.
